(61274, 4824, 0, 1, '時光 旅人', 'which you should be grateful,\r\nat least it''s not grave.\r\nwhich you should be painful,\r\ncause you aren''t going anywhere.\r\n\r\n男vocal:黃以翔\r\n女vocal:許巧宜', '2013-02-27 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, '--------------------\r\nTimer 時光 旅人\r\n--------------------\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you know death better than life,\r\nyou are free to go.\r\nIf you know life better than death,\r\nyou are free to go.\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you don''t know any of them,\r\nI am sorry my pal,\r\nyou can''t go anywhere, but here.\r\n\r\n\r\nA place that keep you suffer,\r\nbut also keep you safe.\r\nwhich you should be grateful,\r\nat least it''s not grave.\r\nwhich you should be painful,\r\ncause you aren''t going anywhere.\r\n\r\n\r\nI am no g-d, and no fiend,\r\njust a friend that you can''t credited.\r\nI know death better than life, \r\nI know life better than death;\r\nhowever my pal, who wander in between, \r\nI am sorry the traveler, you''re my slave.\r\n\r\n\r\nA place that keep you suffer,\r\nbut also keep you safe.\r\nwhich you should be grateful,\r\nat least it''s not grave.\r\nwhich you should be painful,\r\ncause you aren''t going anywhere.', '', 257, '', '黃以翔', '陳彥伶', '黃以翔', '', '', 0, 1, 1, '2013-02-27 14:48:45', '2013-10-07 17:24:05', '2013-05-09 03:42:33'),
(61275, 4824, 0, 1, '今夜我們都是伍佰 - 白鴿Dove(live改編版)', '今夜我們都是伍佰 - 白鴿Dove(live改編版)', '2013-02-27 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, ' 伍佰\r\n\r\n白鴿\r\n\r\n作詞：伍佰\r\n\r\n前方啊　沒有方向\r\n身上啊　沒有了衣裳\r\n鮮血啊　滲出了翅膀\r\n我的眼淚　溼透了胸膛\r\n飛翔著　強忍著傷\r\n逃離了　獵人的槍\r\n我的雙腳　沒有了知覺\r\n我的心情　下冰冷的雪\r\n\r\n親愛的母親　摯愛的朋友\r\n沉默的大地　沉默的天空\r\n\r\n縱然帶著永遠的傷口\r\n至少我還擁有自由\r\n飛翔啊　飛在天空\r\n用力吹吧　無情的風\r\n我不會害怕　也無須懦弱\r\n流浪的路　我自己走\r\n那是種驕傲　陽光的灑脫\r\n白雲從我腳下掠過\r\n縱然帶著永遠的傷口\r\n至少我還擁有自由\r\n乾枯的身影　憔悴的面容\r\n揮著翅膀　不再回頭\r\n縱然帶著永遠的傷口\r\n至少我還擁有自由\r\n飛翔啊　飛在天空\r\n用力吹吧　無情的風\r\n嗚～～', '', 249, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2013-02-27 15:09:16', '2015-03-12 13:59:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
